    "Taking REVERIE as an example, one task example is as follows: Instruction: Go to the lounge on the first level and bring the trinket that's sitting on the fireplace.",
    "Landmarks: 1.first level; 2.lounge; 3.fireplace; 4.trinket.",
    "Through such example, we can let ChatGPT know that it should extract navigational sequential landmarks rather than textual sequential landmarks (1.lounge; 2.first level; 3.trinket; 4.fireplace).",
    "Moreover, it should extract \"first level\" as the landmark rather than \"level\".",
    "After in-context learning with task examples, we can ask ChatGPT to extract Text Encoder Cross-Modal Transformer Encoder Action Prediction Observations Landmark cooccurrence priors 1. bathroom: bathtub, toilet, sink,... 2. kitchen: stove, oven, sink,... 3. kitchen island: kitchen, counter, stove,..."
